Class LoginDatabase

java.lang.Object
br.net.dd.netherwingcore.database.common.GenericDatabase<LoginDatabaseStatements>
br.net.dd.netherwingcore.database.implementation.LoginDatabase
public class LoginDatabase extends GenericDatabase<LoginDatabaseStatements>
LoginDatabase is a singleton class that extends GenericDatabase to handle database operations specific to the login database.
